{"tid":2095184,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(分化師) 教你如何將令大陸民眾嘅仇恨spin去香港警察","createTime":"2020-07-05T09:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:13:49.000Z","uid":222970,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9733a173ef606e5d0f02668f2c04945607a9b25d","tid":2095184,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"首先你係一個撐警藍絲<br />\n<br />\n我地全部支持香港警察取代大陸公安！<br />\n<br />\n要不斷煲大警察既人工 去貶低大陸公安人工<br />\n<br />\n警察月薪 計埋OT 5萬以上 公安得6000一個月<br />\n<br />\n然後係微博撐警 不斷讚警察效率狂踩大陸公安<br />\n<br />\n學歷 紀律 專業操守 EQ IQ 任何方面<br />\n<br />\n狂讚警察 狂踩公安解放軍 踩到佢地一文不值<br />\n<br />\n再係抖音整片拎警察同公安作對比<br />\n<br />\n佢封一個微博ac 再開10個<br />\n<br />\n不斷分化佢地 每日都要分化!!!!!!!! <br />\n<br />\n每一秒都要分化佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港警察同中國公安<br />\n人工對比</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7CR2aU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7CR2aU.png&h=b05afd0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港警察展現專業精神 <br />\n中國公安展現偷懶精神</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vL67Awc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvL67Awc.png&h=5c22c4c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4559474ca0b23f28339b64a0f62b14a5f6412039","tid":2095184,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"高質post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「震惊3万人」 原来广东公安月入5000！港𤌴末日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2095078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2095078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"511229dd0b77b63336914384fa9f3c1dedd794af","tid":2095184,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTim